# Employee Lookup Console App (C# + MySQL)

This is a simple C# console application that connects to a MySQL database to search for employees by their ID.

## Features

- Connects to a MySQL database using `MySql.Data`
- Uses `async/await` for non-blocking database access
- Retrieves employee details by their GUID (ID)
- Gracefully handles errors like invalid input or failed database connections

## Technologies Used

- C# (.NET)
- MySQL
- ADO.NET (`MySql.Data` NuGet package)

